The paper deals with natural language processing and proposes a neural model for recognizing lexical semantic relations between word pairs. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the arXiv category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). The paper also mentions unsupervised learning, which is a common topic in the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper proposes a method for extracting features, which is a common topic in the sub-category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with corpus analysis, which is a common topic in the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper proposes a neural model, which is a common topic in the sub-category of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
